contentrichtext.text: {{orphan|date=July 2009}}{{Taxobox | image = | image_caption = | regnum = [[Animal]]ia | phylum = [[Arthropod]]a | classis = [[Insect]]a | ordo = [[Fly|Diptera]] | familia = [[Ulidiidae]] | genus = ''[[Xanthacrona]]'' | species = '''''X. phyllochaeta''''' | binomial = ''Xanthacrona phyllochaeta'' | subdivision_ranks = Subspecies | subdivision = }} '''''Xanthacrona phyllochaeta''''' is a species of ulidiid or picture-winged fly in the genus ''[[Xanthacrona]]'' of the family [[Ulidiidae]].<ref>[http://www.itis.gov/servlet/SingleRpt/SingleRpt]</ref><ref>[http://nomen.at/Xanthacrona phyllochaeta]</ref><ref>http://data.gbif.org/species/browse/taxon/13143053</ref> ==References== {{Reflist}} {{DEFAULTSORT:Xanthacrona Phyllochaeta}} [[Category:Ulidiidae]] {{Ulidiidae-stub}}
